name: i_have_love_poem.png
description:
this is mi genesis, continued. 
(TW: grief) 
abt a month later, by the time i had the energy to write a poem to go w the title i'd drafted, i was fully immersed in the nft-scape, which had given me more hope than i'd felt in months. 
i regularly dealt w (& still do) heart-hallowing grief but, at the very least, i had remembered that i was not alone. 
i hope i dn't forget.
